title: 2019 Week 9 Recap
itunes:title: 2019 Week 9 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap every game that happened in Week 9 starting with the Chiefs pulling a big win off against the Vikings (3:39) and a missed field goal for the Colts that will keep Vinatieri up at night. (09:44). The Chargers pulled off a big win against the Packers (30:45) and the heroes react to the Browns (56:09) and Jets loses (1:02:58). The heroes close the show by recapping the Ravens steamrolling over the Patriots in the Sunday Night Football game. (01:15:23)
